Author: boo_snug
Text: It’s okay friend. You’re not a waste. I know your friend was glad to have you there and to be with you. You’re a great person and a great friend, don’t forget that.

Author: Dalos_
Text: It’s okay, love. You’re doing the best you can and right now you’re struggling. This isn’t a fault and this doesn’t make you a bad person. I promise.
